Package: dppca
Title: Differentially Private PCA Score Plots and Histograms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Yejin", "Jo", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for performing (optionally differentially private) PCA 
    and visualizing 2D score plots and histograms, including group-wise 
    DP histograms and sampling from DP histograms.
